-- H.I.G. Capital Raises 825 Million Euros for Private Equity Fund
-- B y   K i e l   P o r t e r
-- 2013-07-02T08:50:04Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-07-02/h-i-g-capital-raises-825-million-euros-for-private-equity-fund.html
H.I.G. Capital LLC raised 825 million
euros ($1.1 billion) for its second European private equity
fund.  “The fund will follow the strategy of its predecessor
fund, focusing on private equity, buyout and growth capital
investments in lower middle-market companies primarily in
Western Europe,” H.I.G. said in a statement today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
